node.text:
Since people seem to enjoy my art style, I figure I'd post this speed paint (well, speed drawing) of Jootjoot from the previous post. I use a simple charcoal brush for both lining and shading, no effects or special layers anything because I'm a scrub and I do basic ass things. This took 1h15min, and this style is somewhere between my polished style and sketch style.

#thesnipster #jjba #jojosbizarreadventure #jojo #speeddrawing #speedpaint #jotarokujo #jotaro #blackandwhite #doodle #fanart #artistsoninstagram

node.text:
Star Platinum's thoughts about his small, angry, potty mouthed Stand User.

Since the last time I posted, I found and moved to a new apartment. Some stupid shit is always happening in my life lol (just got into car insurance troubles the first week we moved to the new place, I'm not joking) but I'm doing my best and I'm very grateful for everyone for being so patient and supportive. You know me, speed is never my strong points and I can't post as regularly as a lot of other artists, so I can only focus on delivering my best quality work and hope it is worth it for you to stay.

Everytime I take longer to post, Insta nerfs my engagement and reach, so all support is always appreciated 🥺 If you like this pls remember to like, share, bookmark, comment, etc. anything to support 😔🙏❤️❤️ motivates me to keep drawing and helps me out a lot. I also have a Kofi and Patreon (link in bio) if you wanna support me there ✨

node.text:
Part 2 of 2 of the Part 5 Hospital AU I posted a while back, where Joot was there at the hospital with Pol after his fight with Diavolo. Next installment in this timeline: Joot murders Diavolo in cold blood for hurting his bro ✌️😌

No I swear I didn't slack off for three weeks 😂 I got hit by a triple whammy this May - taxes, unexpected insurance costs, and potential immigration problems that could fuck with my process of getting an US green card. Dealing with all of those took precedent over posting content anywhere. I just sorted out the majority of them last weekend. I'm also actively apartment hunting and a bit tired today, so please don't be mean in the comments 😔

If you enjoyed this, give this some love 😣👉👈❤️ Like, share, add to your stories, save, comment, etc. anything to support, it helps me out a lot and really motivated me to draw more 😔🙏❤️❤️
